{"tid":1442294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:48:23.000Z","uid":41353,"like":126,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b8661a7e04ee9d2f0b96b481406620eec2d70f","tid":1442294,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"如果要死咬住721，821會唔會係一個理想日子?<br />\n<br />\n主要訊息可以係:<br />\n- 警黑合作，毒打平民<br />\n- 官黑勾結，鄉黑治港<br />\n- 元朗警察，徇私枉法<br />\n<br />\n地點行動等大家集思廣益"},{"pid":"3b3e70fdba987aa8cfda732b97a90b58c8b8720a","tid":1442294,"uid":182406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭最大死穴 咬住721 千祈唔好停<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441997</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d1dfb938d79f2addd6c5747ab37606951479ac3","tid":1442294,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b7f9b9b7e33ccd287d5d4f8e651d1dbf72f7b6","tid":1442294,"uid":289750,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"係都叫元朗建國記念日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07b76791d3598be031f4a36417561e50e1084d9","tid":1442294,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0&amp;oe=5DDE6B2B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3D85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0%26oe%3D5DDE6B2B&h=61e168b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖主義標籤係多國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名。正名警隊嘅恐怖主義絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=044e454b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">44,009</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 10:11）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本識 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span>"},{"pid":"891cb2780b49532a8f38313cbc81de8e668efb95","tid":1442294,"uid":16029,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"前後搞呢和平示威？<br />\n<br />\n仲象徵政府成個月都未拉到人"},{"pid":"3bf6886f3bfe166d4c8cdf2d466d5a40b5c5b509","tid":1442294,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議正名為「反警黑恐怖治國 反恐遊行/集會」</span>"},{"pid":"33825397218f7b73c289f4e71a6fc3cd77dced53","ti